comments: Capela (HOU) makes marginal contact with Bullock (LAL) as he disengages from the pick.
Ingram (LAL) is already in Paul's (HOU) path when contact occurs and he gives him room to avoid the contact.
James (LAL) establishes himself in a legal guarding position outside of the restricted area and Harden (HOU) drives through and dislodges him.
Ingram (LAL) establishes himself in a picking position in the path of Tucker (HOU) and he absorbs the contact.

LLS shows Hart (LAL) makes slight contact with Paul's (HOU) head during his shot attempt near the rim.   Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.

James (LAL) inadvertently makes contact with Rivers' (HOU) head.  Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Ingram (LAL) moves his foot heel-to-toe to create space.  The official is looking for any potential illegal contact and does not pick-up the pivot foot.
All technical fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
All technical fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
Paul (HOU) makes contact to the wrist of Ingram (LAL) during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Capela (HOU) establishes himself in a picking position in the path of Ingram (LAL) and has his arms extended, but the contact is marginal when he disengages from the pick.
Paul (HOU) commits a take foul on Kuzma (LAL).
